Text: Dashboard and Internet Explorer upgrade Houston Cc Monday December th a new version of the Marketing Dashboard will be rolled out In order for this new version of The Dashboard to work you will need to have Internet Explorer IE loaded on your system If you already have IE PLEASE RESPOND to this message with a confirmation that you have IE or higher loaded No other action on your part is necessary If you DO NOT have IE please follow the instructions below to install it then respond to this email that IE has been loaded If you are uncomfortable doing the upgrade alone or are unsure what version of IE you have please call the helpdesk and someone will assist you Again please respond to this message ASAP we are looking to have everyone in Houston upgraded by Dec st The total process takes less that minutes If you have any question comments or concerns please contact the helpdesk at Thank you

Re Dashboard and Internet Explorer upgrade HoustonIn the document I sent out this morning Instructions to install Internet explorer The Instructions said to type UCOMMOMieisetupexe in the run dialog box It should have read Ncommonieisetupexe I apologize for any inconvenience this may have caused If you have any problems with or questions about the install please call the help desk at Thank you
